  "helpFaqTitle": "Frequently Asked Questions",
  "helpFaqJoinQuestion": "How do I join a group?",
  "helpFaqJoinAnswer": "To join a group, you need an invite code from someone already in the group. Enter the 6-character code on the join screen and choose your display name and avatar color.",
  "helpFaqStreakQuestion": "How do streaks work?",
  "helpFaqStreakAnswer": "Your streak increases each day you answer the daily question. If you miss a day in a group, your streak for that group resets to zero. Try to maintain your streak to climb the leaderboard!",
  "helpFaqTypesQuestion": "What are the different question types?",
  "helpFaqTypesAnswer": "There are several question types:\n\n• Binary Vote: Choose between two options (Yes/No, A/B)\n• Single Choice: Pick one answer from multiple options\n• Free Text: Write your own response\n• Member Choice: Vote for a group member\n• Duo Choice: Select two group members",
  "helpFaqMultiGroupQuestion": "Can I be in multiple groups?",
  "helpFaqMultiGroupAnswer": "Yes! You can join multiple groups with different invite codes. Use the \"Switch Groups\" option in Settings to change between them, or \"Join Another Group\" to add a new one.",
  "helpFaqAdminQuestion": "How do I become an admin?",
  "helpFaqAdminAnswer": "You become an admin by creating a new group. Admins can create daily questions, manage question sets, and see the admin token for their group.",
  "helpFaqResetQuestion": "When does the daily question reset?",
  "helpFaqResetAnswer": "Each group has its own daily rollover hour managed by the backend. To stay safe, answer as early as possible each day.",
  "helpFaqRevoteQuestion": "Can I change my vote after submitting?",
  "helpFaqRevoteAnswer": "Yes. Re-submitting updates your answer for that question. Your streak only increments on your first answer for that day.",
  "helpFaqInviteQuestion": "How do I invite others to my group?",
  "helpFaqInviteAnswer": "Go to Settings and look at the Group Info section. You can share the invite code directly, show a QR code, or use the Share button to send it via other apps.",
